  "texts": [
    "Generative AI systems can operate in different modalities, including text, code, images, audio, video, molecules, robotics, and business intelligence.",
    "These systems can be unimodal, accepting one type of input, or multimodal, accepting multiple input types.",
    "Various generative AI models, such as GPT-4, OpenAI Codex, and DALL-E, have specific applications in text, code, and image generation.",
    "These models have been integrated into products like Microsoft Office, Google Photos, and Adobe Photoshop.",
    "Smaller models can run on smartphones and personal computers, while larger models with tens of billions of parameters may require accelerators like GPUs or AI accelerator chips."
  ],
